<p class="nx-mt-6 nx-leading-7 first:nx-mt-0">今天我们来介绍下，怎么准备 threejs 的环境.</p>
<h2 class="nx-font-semibold nx-tracking-tight nx-text-slate-900 dark:nx-text-slate-100 nx-mt-10 nx-border-b nx-pb-1 nx-text-3xl nx-border-neutral-200/70 contrast-more:nx-border-neutral-400 dark:nx-border-primary-100/10 contrast-more:dark:nx-border-neutral-400">通过 html 引入<a href="#通过-html-引入" id="通过-html-引入" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"></a></h2>
